1
00:01:18,400 --> 00:01:18,930
Brother.

2
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:19,930
Are you okay?

3
00:01:20,080 --> 00:01:20,800
Are you okay?

4
00:01:20,800 --> 00:01:21,560
Let's go. Go.

5
00:01:21,720 --> 00:01:22,200
Wait.

6
00:01:23,039 --> 00:01:23,680
Jiadong.

7
00:01:23,920 --> 00:01:24,880
I have news about your parents

8
00:01:24,880 --> 00:01:26,520
and the other 54 compatriots.

9
00:01:26,520 --> 00:01:27,920
I've found out about them.

10
00:01:27,920 --> 00:01:29,160
Where?

11
00:01:32,240 --> 00:01:32,800
Where?

12
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:34,320
Where? Where?

13
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:41,120
Mr. Yamada.

14
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:42,680
My men saw with their own eyes

15
00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:43,920
that they went in here.

16
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:45,080
Our men saw it too.

17
00:01:45,640 --> 00:01:46,700
Search carefully.

18
00:01:46,960 --> 00:01:47,759
Don't even let

19
00:01:47,800 --> 00:01:49,000
a single bird fly out.

20
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:50,960
Don't worry, not even a feather can fly out.

21
00:01:50,960 --> 00:01:51,840
Yes. Search.

22
00:01:52,039 --> 00:01:53,240
Hurry. Chen Jiadong,

23
00:01:54,320 --> 00:01:54,920
let's see where

24
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:56,120
you can run this time.

25
00:01:56,800 --> 00:01:58,479
I will catch him myself

26
00:01:59,160 --> 00:02:01,040
and wipe out the Chen family.

27
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,640
I know where they are.

28
00:02:05,240 --> 00:02:05,840
Follow me.

29
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:07,600
Everyone, follow me.

30
00:02:07,600 --> 00:02:08,960
Follow me.

31
00:02:15,720 --> 00:02:16,720
Brother Mingshu.

32
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,079
You are right.

33
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:27,530
I also found some evidence.

34
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:35,800
These animals

35
00:02:36,440 --> 00:02:37,600
actually committed

36
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:38,120
such atrocious acts

37
00:02:38,120 --> 00:02:39,320
twelve years ago.

38
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:40,800
Brother Mingshu.

39
00:02:41,720 --> 00:02:42,840
Let's take this evidence

40
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:43,800
out together.

41
00:02:44,680 --> 00:02:46,440
Let the whole world know

42
00:02:46,440 --> 00:02:47,970
the crimes of the Japanese.

43
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:49,480
Avenge my father

44
00:02:49,920 --> 00:02:50,760
and my mother.

45
00:02:51,760 --> 00:02:52,240
Okay.

46
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:03,260
People inside,

47
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:06,160
come out if you know what's good for you.

48
00:03:06,600 --> 00:03:08,360
I know you are hiding inside.

49
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:10,320
If you don't come out,

50
00:03:10,320 --> 00:03:11,280
we will shoot.

51
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:12,760
Chen Jiadong.

52
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:14,220
We know you are inside.

53
00:03:14,720 --> 00:03:15,720
You can't escape.

54
00:03:16,280 --> 00:03:16,810
Come out.

55
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:18,530
Why is Luo Wang here?

56
00:03:19,560 --> 00:03:20,040
Oh no.

57
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:21,460
It's a trap.

58
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:23,320
I was wondering

59
00:03:23,320 --> 00:03:24,800
why the Japanese didn't kill me.

60
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:26,200
They were using me as bait

61
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:27,490
to lure out Jiadong.

62
00:03:28,480 --> 00:03:29,079
I'm sorry

63
00:03:29,480 --> 00:03:30,520
for dragging you into this.

64
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:31,650
It's fine, Mingshu.

65
00:03:31,880 --> 00:03:33,040
It doesn't matter if we die,

66
00:03:33,040 --> 00:03:34,500
but what about the photos?

67
00:03:35,079 --> 00:03:35,800
At this point,

68
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:37,000
there's only one way.

69
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:38,760
The Japanese probably don't know

70
00:03:38,760 --> 00:03:40,020
how many of us are here.

71
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:41,280
One of us has to stay behind

72
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:42,680
and hide with the photos.

73
00:03:43,120 --> 00:03:44,850
Wait until the Japanese leave,

74
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:46,880
find a chance to escape the tea factory,

75
00:03:46,880 --> 00:03:48,240
and make the photos public.

76
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:48,640
Okay.

77
00:03:48,920 --> 00:03:49,760
Wangshu, you stay.

78
00:03:49,760 --> 00:03:50,120
Go.

79
00:03:50,320 --> 00:03:51,320
No, I disagree.

80
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:52,800
If someone has to stay, it should be you.

81
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:53,640
My brother and I will go out.

82
00:03:53,640 --> 00:03:54,160
No.

83
00:03:54,200 --> 00:03:55,200
How can I let a girl

84
00:03:55,200 --> 00:03:56,120
take the risk? Let's go, Mingshu.

85
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:56,520
Okay.

86
00:03:57,440 --> 00:03:58,240
Stop arguing.

87
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:59,050
Wangshu,

88
00:03:59,160 --> 00:03:59,720
you stay.

89
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:01,160
Remember,

90
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:03,160
you must publish the photos.

91
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:04,330
Brother.

92
00:04:15,040 --> 00:04:16,519
You are the kid who ran away

93
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:17,920
twelve years ago.

94
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:19,000
That's right.

95
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:20,560
I am Chen Xiyan's son,

96
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:21,360
Chen Jiadong.

97
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:22,340
Who are you?

98
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:24,960
My name is Yamada Taro.

99
00:04:25,760 --> 00:04:27,080
It was your father

100
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:28,320
who killed my father,

101
00:04:28,520 --> 00:04:29,640
Yamada Ryoki.

102
00:04:30,640 --> 00:04:31,320
Today,

103
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:32,640
I will make you

104
00:04:33,320 --> 00:04:34,450
pay with your blood.

105
00:04:36,280 --> 00:04:37,400
You used recruitment as a cover

106
00:04:37,400 --> 00:04:38,800
to murder Chinese people

107
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:40,900
and do human experiments on them.

108
00:04:41,400 --> 00:04:42,480
My father only did

109
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,960
what every righteous Chinese person

110
00:04:43,960 --> 00:04:44,680
should do.

111
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:46,650
Luo Wang.

112
00:04:48,200 --> 00:04:50,159
You also have Chinese blood in you.

113
00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:52,480
Why are you helping the Japanese

114
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:53,680
kill Chinese people?

115
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:55,180
Do you have no conscience?

116
00:04:55,760 --> 00:04:57,220
Why waste words with them?

117
00:04:57,400 --> 00:04:58,040
Shoot!

118
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:00,400
Wait.

119
00:05:00,840 --> 00:05:01,900
President Yamada,

120
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:03,490
I have something to say.

121
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:11,090
Lin Mingshu.

122
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:15,460
If you marry your sister to me,

123
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:17,200
I can guarantee you won't die

124
00:05:17,320 --> 00:05:18,250
and leave alive.

125
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:19,890
Is that okay?

126
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:24,000
You son of a bitch.

127
00:05:24,320 --> 00:05:25,440
Keep dreaming.

128
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:26,800
My sister will never

129
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:28,520
marry a scum like you.

130
00:05:29,440 --> 00:05:29,920
Okay.

131
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:32,960
You do it the hard way.

132
00:05:38,880 --> 00:05:39,320
Shoot.

133
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:42,250
I'm sorry, Jiadong,

134
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:45,090
for dragging you into this.

135
00:05:47,640 --> 00:05:49,170
I don't blame you, brother.

136
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:50,600
After all,

137
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:53,700
we've been through life and death together.

138
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:08,780
What are you doing?

139
00:06:09,880 --> 00:06:10,410
Mingshu,

140
00:06:13,400 --> 00:06:14,130
you're here.

141
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:15,360
I was worried sick.

142
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,200
Are you all right?

143
00:06:16,200 --> 00:06:16,760
We're fine.

144
00:06:16,760 --> 00:06:17,200
Dad.

145
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:18,840
Thank goodness you came.

146
00:06:18,840 --> 00:06:19,960
Otherwise, Jiadong and I,

147
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:21,290
we both would have died.

148
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:23,000
Where is Wangshu?

149
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:24,520
Dad, I'm here.

150
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:27,280
Are you okay?

151
00:06:27,280 --> 00:06:27,810
I'm fine.

152
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:28,530
Luowang,

153
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:31,360
you're not on duty at the police station.

154
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:32,690
What are you doing here?

155
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:34,250
Reporting to the chief,

156
00:06:34,640 --> 00:06:35,960
we received a report

157
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:37,840
from the Japanese corporation,

158
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:39,460
saying someone

159
00:06:40,159 --> 00:06:41,890
sneaked into their tea factory

160
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:42,530
to steal.

161
00:06:43,159 --> 00:06:43,640
So,

162
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:45,520
I brought some men over

163
00:06:45,520 --> 00:06:46,850
to take a look together.

164
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:48,280
Really?

165
00:06:49,080 --> 00:06:50,280
What is there to steal

166
00:06:50,280 --> 00:06:52,010
in this abandoned tea factory?

167
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:52,880
I think

168
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:54,840
this is clearly the Japanese

169
00:06:55,280 --> 00:06:56,200
framing us.

170
00:06:57,440 --> 00:06:58,520
Chief Songkan,

171
00:06:59,280 --> 00:07:00,400
that's not right.

172
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:02,360
We, Japanese businessmen,

173
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:03,160
come to Malaya

174
00:07:03,400 --> 00:07:04,530
just to do business.

175
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:07,640
Your Malayan police station

176
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:09,160
should protect our

177
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:09,960
property.

178
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:12,000
Mr. Yamada,

179
00:07:12,520 --> 00:07:13,520
what did you lose?

180
00:07:16,320 --> 00:07:17,520
A misunderstanding.

181
00:07:17,640 --> 00:07:18,200
A misunderstanding.

182
00:07:18,200 --> 00:07:19,840
Mr. Yamada, it's a misunderstanding.

183
00:07:19,840 --> 00:07:21,600
Chief, it's all a misunderstanding.

184
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:22,660
They can leave now.

185
00:07:23,880 --> 00:07:24,440
We can go.

186
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:25,960
Hold on, Director Songkan.

187
00:07:25,960 --> 00:07:26,620
There is...

188
00:07:26,960 --> 00:07:28,320
We'll talk about it when we get back.

189
00:07:28,320 --> 00:07:29,080
Alright, alright.

190
00:07:29,080 --> 00:07:31,240
Since it's a misunderstanding, let's disperse.

191
00:07:31,240 --> 00:07:32,500
But you must remember,

192
00:07:32,880 --> 00:07:34,840
on our land in Malaya,

193
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:37,530
we will not tolerate such insolence from you.

194
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:38,560
Okay.

195
00:07:39,280 --> 00:07:40,540
I'll keep that in mind.

196
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:42,250
However, this place

197
00:07:42,400 --> 00:07:44,330
is ultimately Japanese property.

198
00:07:46,440 --> 00:07:47,240
Do as you wish.

199
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:48,440
I won't see you out.

200
00:07:48,440 --> 00:07:48,970
Luowang,

201
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:50,360
hurry up and take your men

202
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:51,560
and leave this place.

203
00:07:51,880 --> 00:07:52,320
Yes.

204
00:07:57,320 --> 00:07:57,850
Let's go.

205
00:08:03,320 --> 00:08:05,120
Since it's a misunderstanding.

206
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:06,060
Mr. Lin,

207
00:08:06,440 --> 00:08:08,040
take Wangshu and Jiadong

208
00:08:08,520 --> 00:08:09,520
and go back first.

209
00:08:09,880 --> 00:08:10,480
Thank you.

210
00:08:11,320 --> 00:08:12,120
Let's go home.

211
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:20,040
Hassan.

212
00:08:21,960 --> 00:08:22,690
Send someone

213
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:24,600
to keep an eye on this Chen Jiadong

214
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:26,660
and those from Wansheng Post Office.

215
00:08:27,080 --> 00:08:27,840
They already know

216
00:08:27,840 --> 00:08:28,600
our secret.

217
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,130
They must

218
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:31,480
have some evidence

219
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:32,340
in their hands.

220
00:08:32,760 --> 00:08:34,220
You must get it back for me.

221
00:08:35,640 --> 00:08:36,039
Yes,

222
00:08:36,480 --> 00:08:37,140
President.

223
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:37,880
Also,

224
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:40,559
about today's incident,

225
00:08:40,559 --> 00:08:41,760
no one is allowed to leak

226
00:08:41,760 --> 00:08:42,760
a single word.

227
00:08:43,400 --> 00:08:45,130
If the headquarters finds out,

228
00:08:45,160 --> 00:08:46,040
we're all dead.

229
00:08:47,040 --> 00:08:47,900
U-Understood.

230
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:53,000
Chen Jiadong.

231
00:08:54,760 --> 00:08:55,920
I will make sure

232
00:08:55,920 --> 00:08:56,840
you die by my hands.
